title: Bullies and Beauty
description:
Sadie welcomes Emma Jenkins to the podcast. Emma is a speaker and writer, who shares her advice from her mom about how fearing people will keep you from God's purpose for your life. She also shares her amazing passion for the Bible and how to dance with Jesus in your everyday life.
